{"tid":2171614,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"變相對政府信任公投","createTime":"2020-08-24T05:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T05:26:50.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"64454ca416a2f29d809f583c94f19106e8ff5edc","tid":2171614,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:25:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/RP4VR7KDQFCP7MZE2W3T6HIGZM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FRP4VR7KDQFCP7MZE2W3T6HIGZM%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsokJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=d74c3abd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200824%2FRP4VR7KDQFCP7MZE2W3T6HIGZM%2F&h=e229dcbe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200824/RP4VR7KDQFCP7MZE2W3T6HIGZM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n變相對政府信任公投<br />\n<br />\n【拆局】雖然特首林鄭月娥聲稱並沒有為全民武漢肺炎檢測定下人數目標，但由昨日官媒《人民日報》發功威嚇，指誰阻礙、抹黑檢測就是與民為敵，以及食物及衞生局長陳肇始等一眾司局長發文配合軟硬兼施。有民主派人士更指，今次全民自願檢測，其實已變相成為港人對林鄭政府一次信心投票，「有幾多港人肯自願去驗，正好反映仲有幾多人對林鄭政府仲有信心。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：陳肇始威逼港人驗毒： 全民不檢測 限聚不放寬<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/bk3ZOUuPQg9kTXgSav-WT6DApE0=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BYS5HS4CRVGNDD4JJDT35N2IIM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fbk3ZOUuPQg9kTXgSav-WT6DApE0%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBYS5HS4CRVGNDD4JJDT35N2IIM.jpg&h=12d38586&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林鄭月娥 資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n人數少過110萬難交代<br />\n<br />\n該民主派人士指，早前林鄭在記者會指，政府推出的全民檢測計劃遭人抹黑、受分化及陰謀論攻擊，希望傳媒可客觀正面報道，但林鄭迴避了最核心問題：為何政府掌握最多宣傳渠道、大部份主流媒體支持政府之下，「仲有咁多人信陰謀論？政府咁易俾人抹黑？咪因為成個政府公信力破產、冇人信政府。」<br />\n<br />\n他更直言，今次全城自願檢測，就如一次港人對政府信心投票，「信政府、信林鄭自然會去做；唔信佢哋就梗唔會做」，笑言整。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"b24de7b935957bc9252f023f4595f7db23e3cd63","tid":2171614,"uid":13503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T05:26:50.000Z","msg":"果件乜鳩銅心口罩已經係公投<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}